\id JUD Lugulu Bible Version
\h Yuda
\toc1 Ibaluwa iyandikighwe na Yuda
\toc2 Yuda
\toc3 Yud
\mt2 Ibaluwa iyandikighwe na
\mt1 Yuda
\imt1 Ichilongole
\ip Ibaluwa ino yokemighwa Yuda kwaapfila imunu iyandike kokemighwa Yuda. Yuda kolonga yeye ka ndughu wa Yakobu iyakalile ndughu wa Mtwatsa Yesu. Apfo yotogholighwa Yuda naye ndughu wa Yesu (Yuda 1). Ng'atumanya bae ka ibaluwa ino tsaibamighwa kutumighwa kwa kanisa limwe, lekeni kwa aghala ighali mna Laghano lya Ghumwande, yakoneka iwanu wa mwanduso ghendo iwandikilighwe na Yuda iwo Wayahudi. “Hata apfo ibaluwa yake yolangusa kawandikila awala iwakemighwe, iwanoghelighwe na Aba Imulungu na kwikighwa kwaajili ya Yesu Kiristu” (Yuda 1). Pfipfila ibaluwa ino yolangusa ka yandikighwa mna ghumwaka ghwa sitini kulawa Yesu hakalile muisi.
\ip Na ichinu chikulu chabamile mne ibaluwa ino, kuwakanya Wakiristu wose waleke kuwawinza iwalangulitsi waghutsu (Yuda 4). Pfipfila mne ibaluwa ino mna mbuli itsighala na atsila itsili mne ibaluwa ya keli ya Petiri, itsilangusa mbuli tsa iwalangulitsi waghutsu (Yuda 4, 2 Petiri 2:1), na mbuli tsa wamalaika na ghumji ghwa Sodoma na Gomora.
\iot Ighali mno
\io1 Mne ghumstali ghwa 1-2, Yuda kakwandusa kwa kulonga yeye yali nani na kuwalombela iwosoma ibaluwa yake.
\io1 Mne ghumstali ghwa 3-4, kowalongela ichinu ichitendile mbaka kakwandika ibaluwa ino, ukuwakanya iwanu kwa mbuli tsa iwalangulitsi waghutsu.
\io1 Mne ghumstali ghwa 5-16, kowalangusa mbuli tse iwanu, na aghala ighalawile mne Laghano lya Ghumwande.
\io1 Mne ghumstali ghwa 17-23, kowalongela pfawobamighwa ukwalangitsa na ghamalangulitso gha ughutsu.
\io1 Mne ghumstali ghwa 24-25, Yuda komalitsila kwa kumtunya Imulungu.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nene Yuda mtumwa wa Yesu Kiristu, na mdodo wake Jakobu.
\p Nomwandikilani mwemwe yamkemighwe ne Imulungu na yamnoghelighwa na Aba Imulungu, na yamlolesighwa na Yesu Kiristu.
\p 
\v 2 Nomlomba Imulungu yawongetsele libatsi na unoghelo wake, na yamwikeni tseghamba.
\s1 Walangulitsi waghutsu
\p 
\v 3 Sale tsangu, nitenda ka pfanidahile kumwandikileni mwemwe mbuli tsa ukombotsi watuhangila, tsambona ghoya kumwandikileni na kuwaghumani mimoyo kwaajili ya ukwamila ukutoghola kwaweng'ighwe iwanu we Imulungu mala lumwe kwa matsuwa ghose.
\v 4 Kwaapfila hana iwanu ing'awompfuka Imulungu iwengile chinyelenyele mghati mwetu, iwanu iwoghalusa usenga we uluso we Imulungu wetu ili wadahe kutenda ughoni, nawo womlema Yesu Kiristu, Mkulu na Imtwatsa wetu yaliyeka. Lekeni kulawa ghumwande Ghamaandiko Mahenzeluka ghalonga ukuhighighwa ikuwabeta iwanu awo.
\p 
\v 5 Hata ka mwomanya agha ghose, nobama nimkumbuseni Imtwatsa pfayawakombole iwanu wake kulawa isi ya Misiri, lekeni hambele kawakoma awala iwalemile kutoghola.
\v 6 Na wamalaika iwalekile ukulu wawo, na kuleka kaye yawo ya mwanduso, Imulungu kaweka mchisi na kuwoha kwa iminyororo kwa ghamatsuwa ghose ili wahighighwe mna litsuwa lila kulu.
\v 7 Pfipfila Sodoma na Gomola na imiji ili habehi. Tsawatenda ughoni, na iwanu wasulukila ng'uli tsa weyawo, wahighighwa kukala mne ghumoto wa ghamatsuwa ghose, ili iwanu welangulitse kulawa mna agho.
\p 
\v 8 Pfipfila ukulota kwawo kwowalongotsa mna kutsitenda ng'uli tsawo tsihe, woulema ukulu we Imulungu na wopfiligha pfilumbe pfikulu pfa kulanga.
\v 9 Hata malaika mkulu Mikaeli, hesongile na kwihisanya na Yehile kwaajili ya lukuli lwa Musa, ng'aghetsile bae kumlongeletsela kwa kumligha, ila kalonga, “Imtwatsa mwenyegho yakukembele!”
\v 10 Lekeni iwanu wano woghaligha aghala ghang'awaghamanyile bae. Hana pfinu pfawomanya na wopfitenda bila kupfikitsa ka iwanyama iwalihela tsimbutsi pfawotenda, na pfinu apfo pfowahinya wawo wenyegho.
\v 11 Watsoghaya! Iwanu awo waiwinza nzila iila ya Kaini, waliwinza totso lya Balaamu kwa ukumota kwawo. Watotsa ka pfayatotsile Kora na wakomighwa ka pfayakomighwe Kora.
\v 12 Iwanu awo wakuja namwe bila chinyala mne ipfihungo pfenu pfa unoghelo. Weghala na mabambalawe ghehile ighodaha kuihinya imeli, wawo ka iwadimi iweghutitsa iwenyegho waliheka. Weghala ne ghamawingu ighalihela mvula, ighoghulusighwa na libeho, weghala ne imibiki ilihela ghamatunda chipindi cho ukupfuna, iing'olighwe na iinyalile ghendo.
\v 13 Iwanu awo weghala na ghamawimbi makulu gha ibahali, na ghamatendo ghawo ghe chinyala gholawa ka lihopfu. Iwanu awo ka tsinondo itsikwangakwanga itsikilighwe chisi cha ghamatsuwa ghose.
\p 
\v 14 Naye Enoki, munu wa lweleko lwa saba kulawa Adamu, tsakatabili mbuli tse iwanu wano, tsakalonga, “Loleni, Imtwatsa kakutsa na wenzeluke wake wengi ng'ani yang'awapeteka bae,
\v 15 kuwahigha iwanu wose, na kuwalangusa iwanu wose yang'awompfuka Imulungu ghehile ghose ghawatendile, na kwa mbuli tsose tsihile iwanu wane nzambi tsawamlongile Imulungu.”
\p 
\v 16 Iwanu wano wong'ung'ula na wolonga chaka, wotenda ghehile ka pfawobama, weghoda na wowatunya ng'ani iwanu wangi kwa faida yawo wenyegho.
\s1 Makanyo na malaghitso
\p 
\v 17 Lekeni ndughu tsangu, mleke kwisemwa ghamlongelighwe ghumwande ne iwatumighwa wa Imtwatsa wetu Yesu Kiristu.
\v 18 Tsawawalongelani, “Mna ghamatsuwa gha ukutsigha watsolawila iwanu ing'awompfuka Imulungu, iwanu iwowinza tsitamaa tsawo tsihile watsowakilani.”
\v 19 Iwanu awo iwo iwotenda iwanu weghole, wawo wokwalangula pfinu pfe iisi, wahela Ghumuhe ghwe Imulungu.
\v 20 Lekeni mwemwe, sale tsangu, mwongetse ukutoghola kwenu ikwenzeluke ghendo na mlombe kwa ngupfu ya Ghumuhe Mwenzeluka.
\v 21 Kaleni mne unoghelo we Imulungu aku mwombetetsa Imtwatsa wetu Yesu Kiristu, kwa libatsi lyake katsowaghaleni mne ughima wa ghamatsuwa ghose.
\p 
\v 22 Woneleni libatsi iwanu wala iwopfukapfuka,
\v 23 wakweng'uleni iwanu wangi kulawa mne ghumoto, na woneleni libatsi iwanu wangi aku mwalangitse, mtsihile tsitamaa tsawo tsihile itsiutenda ughima wawo uhinyike.
\s1 Ghamalombi gha ukumtunya Imulungu
\p 
\v 24 Yeye kodaha kumwapfilani mleke ukughwa, na kuwaghalani mbaka hambele he utunitso wake aku mwahela matotso na kwa kudeng'elela ng'ani,
\v 25 Imulungu yaliyeka Mkombotsi wetu yatunyighwe, yane ukulu na ngupfu na uwetso kubitila Yesu Kiristu Imtwatsa wetu, kulawa ghumwande ng'ana iisi ilumbighwe bae, leloli na ghamatsuwa ghose ighakutsa! Amina.
